{"tid":535503,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"成龍黐撚線動作特技","createTime":"2018-01-21T03:01:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-21T04:33:50.000Z","uid":134683,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"041b3df30b625630b92335dc9207dbe046d01d5f","tid":535503,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T03:01:16.000Z","msg":"以前個成龍簡直黐線到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喺行緊既巴士上面做幾個危險動作、商場內攬柱滑落4層直插入玻璃屋、由摩天輪爬落地面、凌空避開飛車...<br />\n呢d場面是旦一次出意外已經冇命<br />\n最恐怖係八幾年拍龍兄虎弟重傷幾乎死得<br />\n好返之後都未識死繼續拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔計佢為人<br />\n全世界好可能得佢一個會親身上陣拍咁多年危險動作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FgOREa1H5u8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFgOREa1H5u8&d=irIEEVvA7ca%2BemMB6FcfETCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=77718e2b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FgOREa1H5u8</a>"},{"pid":"05573ea4796f7b5696bf2b344742366e00316e35","tid":535503,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T03:04:28.000Z","msg":"原來已經有人講緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a9ab10a14c6cbe11864a5ec5cd832a1ca74810f","tid":535503,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T03:45:09.000Z","msg":"佢現實生活係咪都跳嚟跳去"},{"pid":"e66d3a24dbce19d63e3adb92f530bf784c9ce074","tid":535503,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T04:12:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75304ad467f17fd7482cbb6bd310b21fb86b190a","tid":535503,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05573ea4796f7b5696bf2b344742366e00316e35","tid":535503,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T03:04:28.000Z","msg":"原來已經有人講緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"rep